ikhail Voronin]], Russian gymnast (b. 1945)\n*[[2005]] &ndash; [[Charilaos Florakis]], Greek politician (b. 1914)\n*  2005   &ndash; [[Thurl Ravenscroft]], American voice actor and singer (b. 1914)\n*[[2006]] &ndash; [[Lee Jong-wook]], South Korean physician and diplomat (b. 1945)\n*[[2007]] &ndash; [[Pemba Doma Sherpa]], Nepalese mountaineer (b. 1970)\n*[[2008]] &ndash; [[Robert Asprin]], American soldier and author (b. 1946)\n*[[2010]] &ndash; [[Martin Gardner]], American mathematician, cryptographer, and author (b. 1914)\n*[[2011]] &ndash; [[Joseph Brooks (songwriter)|Joseph Brooks]], American director, producer, screenwriter, and composer (b. 1938)\n*[[2012]] &ndash; [[Muzafar Bhutto]], Pakistani politician (b. 1970)\n*  2012   &ndash; [[Wesley A. Brown]], American lieutenant and engineer (b. 1927)\n*[[2013]] &ndash; [[Sigurd Ottovich Schmidt]], Russian historian and ethnographer (b. 1922)\n*  2013 &ndash; [[Murder of Lee Rigby|Lee Rigby]], British fusilier\n*[[2015]] &ndash; [[Marques Haynes]], American basketball player and coach (b. 1926)\n*  2015   &ndash; [[Vladimir Katriuk]], Ukrainian-Canadian [[SS]] officer (b. 1921)\n*[[2016]] &ndash; [[Bata \u017divojinovi\u0107|Velimir \"Bata\" \u017divojinovi\u0107]], Serbian actor and politician (b. 1933)\n*[[2017]] &ndash; [[Nicky Hayden]], American professional motorcycle racer (b. 1981)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/motor/2017/05/17/superbike-race-nicky-hayden-hit-by-car-bicycle-italy/101803180/|title=American Superbike rider Nicky Hayden hit by car while cycling|website=[[USA Today]]|date=2017-05-17|access-date=2020-02-28}}</ref>\n*[[2019]] &ndash; [[Judith Kerr]], German-born British writer and illustrator (b. 1923)\n<!-- Please do not add non-notable people, fictional characters, or people without Wikipedia articles to this list. No red links, please. Do not link multiple occurrences of the same year, just link the first occurrence. If there are multiple people in the same birth year